data.description: Fabulous 5 bedroom home in the MAIZE school district. This spacious home is move in ready and boasts plenty of space for your family. and friends. The kitchen has granite countertops and a breakfast nook that is connected to a beautiful back deck. The open concept living and dining make entertaining for holidays or parties a breeze. The main floor boasts a split floor plan with a stunning primary bedroom and remodeled en suite bath, large walk-in closet and access to the large deck. The basement features a huge family room with view out to the back yard. Two bedrooms, a full bathroom  and plenty of storage complete the basement. This amazing home is close to shopping, dining, and entertainment and is located in the desireable Maize school district. All kitchen appliances stay. The above ground pool, trampoline and playset are all negotiable. Don't wait, schedule your showing today! Photos Coming Soon!
